title: #93: Tamra's White Trash Wedding & Fake Pennies
description:
This week, Matt Whitfield (Yahoo) and Ronnie Karam (TrashTalkTV) make fun of Tamra's inability to play nice, Real Housewives of New Jersey's lame attempts to draw out their fambly dramz, and Real Housewives of Miami's need for violence.

Chat with us live during the show on our facebook page: http://www.facebook.com/watchwhatcrappens
These are live on Tues at 430 Pacific. We also do a Big Brother Podcast live on Thurs nights at 7:30 Pacific here on our Youtube page: http://www.youtube.com/thetvclique

For Big Brother Video Speed Recaps join Ronnie on YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/trashtalkteevee
For hilarious tomato drama, join Ben on YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/bsideblog
